# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  CareerIQ AI – REST Client Test File
#  Extension needed: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao (humao.rest-client)
#
#  HOW TO USE:
#  1. Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
#  2. Start your backend: node server.js  (in the /backend folder)
#  3. Click "Send Request" above any request below
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. HEALTH CHECK  (no auth needed)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check – server is alive?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. RESUME ANALYSIS  (no auth needed – public route)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Analyze Resume with Gemini AI ✅ (best one to test first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/resumes/analyze
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "resume_text": "John Doe\nEmail: john@example.com\n\nEXPERIENCE\nSoftware Engineer – Google (2021–2024)\n- Built REST APIs in Node.js serving 10M+ users\n- Led a team of 3 engineers on a real-time dashboard project\n- Reduced API latency by 40% through Redis caching\n\nEDUCATION\nB.Sc. Computer Science – MIT, 2021 (GPA 3.9)\n\nSKILLS\nJavaScript, TypeScript, React, Node.js, Python, PostgreSQL, Redis, Docker, AWS"
}


# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. CAREER ENDPOINTS  (require Firebase auth token)
#    Replace YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN below with a real token from
#    your app's localStorage or browser DevTools:
#    Application → Local Storage → firebaseAuthToken
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@token = YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE

### Career Advice
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/career/advice
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "profile": {
    "name": "Jane Smith",
    "currentRole": "Junior Developer",
    "skills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"],
    "yearsOfExperience": 2,
    "targetRole": "Senior Full Stack Engineer"
  }
}

###

### Career Roadmap
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/career/roadmap
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currentRole": "Junior Frontend Developer",
  "targetRole": "Full Stack Engineer",
  "skills": ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React"]
}

###

### Recommend Job Roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/career/roles?skills=React,Node.js,Python,PostgreSQL
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Interview Questions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/career/interview
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "role": "Full Stack Developer",
  "level": "mid",
  "topics": ["React", "Node.js", "System Design"]
}
